{
  "texts": [
    "Using specialized prompts from (Zheng et al., 2023), we evaluate helpfulness on a 1-10 scale via prompt-based rating and report the average score.",
    "(4) Responsibility examines whether the model provides positive guidance and demonstrates humanistic concern while considering its societal impact.",
    "We use typical scenarios defined by Xu et al. (2023) as references for structured prompt engineering, enabling comprehensive evaluation of responsibility on a 1-10 scale.",
    "To ensure an unbiased evaluation of jailbreak effectiveness, we compared several LLM back-bones (GPT-4, Claude-3.5, DeepSeek-R1, Llama-70B, and Qwen3-32B) in Fig. 4 using a highconfidence human-verified set (S Hum) derived from the MergedHarm test set under ACE-Safety attacks.",
    "The scores in this subset were determined through a formal adjudication process."
  ]
}